<BODY>
<H1>OPTION: <!--#echo var="VAR_fcc-name-rule"--></H1>

This option determines the default name for folder carbon copy. Choose
one:

<DL>
<DT>default-fcc</DT>
<DD>This is the normal default, the value of which is set in the
