 Fullname  : Bedrock Elders
 Fcc       :
 Comment   :
 Addresses : flint@bedrock.org,
             rubble@bedrock.org
</PRE>
<P>
instead. Note the difference in the Addresses field.
<P>
&lt;End of help on this topic&gt;
</BODY></HTML>
