</UL><P>
&lt;End of help on this topic&gt;
</BODY>
</HTML>
====== h_config_enable_view_addresses =====
<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>FEATURE: <!--#echo var="FEAT_enable-msg-view-addresses"--></TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1>FEATURE: <!--#echo var="FEAT_enable-msg-view-addresses"--></H1>

